::Chaostaur::
       "Hmm.  It shouldn't be too hard to rework my guns.  Give me a few 
minutes."  He puts his blasters on the ground and starts fiddling around.  
"Hey!  It has the capability but it isn't easy to switch back and forth.  
Tell me now what you need me to do and I'll work on it."
